         MACRO                                                                  
         CATCODE &STR,&COMM                                                     
         GBLA   &NCONST                                                         
         GBLC   &LABEL(25),&DESC(25)                                            
&NCONST  SETA   &NCONST+1                                                       
&LABEL(&NCONST) SETC '&STR'                                                     
&DESC(&NCONST)  SETC '&COMM'(2,K'&COMM-2)                                       
         MEND                                                                   
